Calendar extension "cz_simple_cal"
     ______________________________________________________________________________________

Introduction

Caution

   This extension in alpha state.

   The current version is only compatible with TYPO3 4.5 LTS and the corresponding version of
   extbase (1.3).
   There is a version for TYPO3 4.4 and extbase 1.2 on github in the extbase-1.2 branch. But
   this is deprecated, so don't expect any bugfixes or even new features.

What does it do?

   This extension provides a simple calendar.

Feature List

     * Allday Events
     * Recurring Events
     * Exceptions, Exception Groups
     * Categories
     * adding actions via Typoscript
     * templates using the hCalendar and hCard microformats
     * ...and all the goodness that is Extbase and Fluid.

